Melbourne Storm has finalised its 2018 playing squad ahead of the first group of players starting pre-season training in the first week of November.

Storm today confirmed Sandor Earl, Billy Walters, Harry Grant, Lachlan Timm, Louis Geraghty, Cooper Johns, Sale Finau, Tino Fa’asuamaleaui, Kayleb Milne and Junior Ratuvu have all signed with the Club for the 2018 season.
